{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b8c9d0e1-f2a3-4567-1234-678901234567",
    "name": "Lav60 - Venda Totem",
    "description": "Collection para **criar venda no totem** com créditos do cliente.\n\n## Fluxo\n\n1. Configure variáveis (`x_token`, credenciais, `store_code`, `product_id`, `machine_code`, `sale_value`).\n2. **Login com CPF** → salva JWT.\n3. **Criar Venda Totem**.\n\n## Cálculo do total\n\n`total = value × quantity × número_de_máquinas`\n\nDocumentação: `docs/guides/venda-totem.md`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "serverUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:3100"
    },
    {
      "key": "x_token",
      "value": "SEU_X_TOKEN",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "tax_id_number",
      "value": "05791897405",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "password",
      "value": "sua_senha",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "product_id",
      "value": "a5c18a23-a50a-4afd-91ed-41d7a7864e39",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "machine_code",
      "value": "M01",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "sale_value",
      "value": "15.00",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "sale_quantity",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "soap_type",
      "value": "floral",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "payment_method",
      "value": "credits",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "payment_total",
      "value": "15.00",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "customer_jwt",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "sale_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "storeCode",
      "value": "pb05"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Passo 1 — Login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login com CPF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_jwt', pm.response.json().data.token);",
                  "    pm.test('JWT salvo', () => pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('customer_jwt')).to.not.be.empty);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tax_id_number\": \"{{tax_id_number}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/auth/login"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Passo 2 — Venda",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar Venda Totem",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const value = parseFloat(pm.collectionVariables.get('sale_value'));",
                  "const qty = parseFloat(pm.collectionVariables.get('sale_quantity'));",
                  "const total = (value * qty).toFixed(2);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('payment_total', total);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json().data ?? {};",
                  "    const attrs = data.attributes ?? {};",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('sale_id', data.id);",
                  "    pm.test('Venda criada', () => pm.expect(data.id).to.not.be.empty);",
                  "    console.log('Venda ID:', data.id);",
                  "    console.log('Total: R$', attrs['total-value']);",
                  "    console.log('Loja:', attrs['store-code']);",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 400) {",
                  "    console.warn('400: saldo insuficiente, máquina inválida ou indisponível');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{customer_jwt}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"store_code\": \"{{storeCode}}\",\n  \"released_machine\": false,\n  \"sale_items\": [\n    {\n      \"value\": \"{{sale_value}}\",\n      \"quantity\": \"{{sale_quantity}}\",\n      \"product_id\": \"{{product_id}}\",\n      \"soap_type\": \"{{soap_type}}\",\n      \"machines\": [{ \"code\": \"{{machine_code}}\" }]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"payments\": [\n    {\n      \"value\": \"{{payment_total}}\",\n      \"payment_method\": \"{{payment_method}}\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/sales/totem_sales",
            "description": "Remove `soap_type` do body se não usar amaciante.\n\nConfirme que `machine_code` existe e está disponível na loja."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Fluxo completo",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login com CPF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_jwt', pm.response.json().data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tax_id_number\": \"{{tax_id_number}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Criar Venda Totem",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const total = (parseFloat(pm.collectionVariables.get('sale_value')) * parseFloat(pm.collectionVariables.get('sale_quantity'))).toFixed(2);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('payment_total', total);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{customer_jwt}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"store_code\": \"{{storeCode}}\",\n  \"sale_items\": [{\"value\":\"{{sale_value}}\",\"quantity\":\"{{sale_quantity}}\",\"product_id\":\"{{product_id}}\",\"machines\":[{\"code\":\"{{machine_code}}\"}]}],\n  \"payments\":[{\"value\":\"{{payment_total}}\",\"payment_method\":\"{{payment_method}}\"}]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/sales/totem_sales"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}